      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<div class=\"article-content\">\n<section class=\"article-body\">\n<div class=\"article-content\">\n<section class=\"article-body\">\n<div class=\"article-content\">\n<section class=\"article-body\">\n<h3 id=\"h_01HXYS9SF6KY1EAQ17VRHQQAWX\">Added</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>​<strong><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-31149\">LCD-31149</a> - Download Files Using LCP:</strong> Added a new CLI command to download files from the Liferay service, allowing users to easily access important files like thread dumps.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"h_01HXYS9NRE5H6PTZ9Y99PF8QQH\">Bug Fixes</h3>\n<ul class=\"ak-ul\">\n<li>\n<strong><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-39634\">LCD-39634</a></strong> <strong>- Activities Not Loading in Certain Environments: </strong>Fixed an issue where in certain environments, filtering by general activities on the Activities page would result in no activities found.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>"
      },
